# Backend URL for the mobile app (env-switchable).
#
# Leave these UNSET to use the deployed production backend (default):
#   API:    https://linkloop-server.onrender.com/api
#   Socket: https://linkloop-server.onrender.com
#
# For LOCAL development against the Express server (`npm run dev:server` in the
# web project), copy this file to `.env` and point both at your machine's LAN IP.
# Your phone and PC must be on the same Wi-Fi. Find your IP with `ipconfig`
# (Windows) / `ifconfig` (macOS/Linux) — do NOT use localhost (that's the phone).
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.20:4000/api
# EXPO_PUBLIC_SOCKET_URL=http://192.168.1.20:4000
